author: Hannah (Sensational Sidekick)
title: ToysRUs: Play-Doh Sets Only $1.98 Shipped
text:
Head on over to ToysRUs where you can score great deals on Play-Doh sets . Even sweeter, through tomorrow only, shipping is FREE sitewide on all orders! These would make fun non-candy Easter Basket stuffers.
Here are a few of the deals I spotted… Play-Doh 4-Pack – Party Colors 
Only $1.98 shipped (regularly $3.99)
Play-Doh Star Wars Luke Skywalker and Snowtrooper Can-Heads 
Only $1.98 shipped (regularly $5.99)

Play-Doh Star Wars Mission on Endor Featuring Can-Heads 
Only $3.98 shipped (regularly $7.99)
Play-Doh Mickey Mouse Clubhouse Tools Set 
Only $4.98 shipped (regularly $9.99)

Play-Doh Ice Cream Cone Container 
Only $4.98 (regularly $7.99)
$100 ToysRUs eGift Card only $85 
If you’re tired of filling all those Easter Eggs with candy, here are some other items to consider !
